Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九十六
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九十七
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九十八
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九十九
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人討厭的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:15.80,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,「10月12日  暴風雨的乾燥劑」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天恰逢天公作美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不正是開運動會的絕好天氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家本著文武兼備的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同每日的學習一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓足幹勁向著目標努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停之前先休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（刷牙吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幾號？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.33,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（裝聾做啞時間）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,9…9號喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是問你颱風…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下起雨來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,估計還得下好一陣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天能行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道能不能開運動會的感覺真不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做個圓頂操場的話就不會有因雨中止這事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圓頂操場？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了圓頂操場的話體育館的立足之地不就沒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,體育館裡是地板嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校庭的圓頂操場可是地面喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  這是不可能實現的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不會這麼快集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點想上洗手間去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（職員室）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金…金太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…呃…剛才…這個…那個…在那邊…呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你去過洗手間了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那待會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎停雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以運動會重新開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也是我們白組會贏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這五年來都是白組連續獲勝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是哪位啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B班的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去年要是我出場絕對是紅組的勝利的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐  去年怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腮腺炎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高中生還…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  不要懶懶散散的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.43,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（廣播部）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,齊唱校歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:28.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（山吹高中）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺自己突然跑得飛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,換作這邊的話腳步就異常沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.57,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過換回來的又可以飛奔了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,換作這邊就沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這邊的話又跑得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  會挨訓的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼由乃也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又下起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,選手宣誓之後就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,選手代表請上前來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.14,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（人聲嘈雜）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搶劫運動員船隻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.47,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：她本想說“遵循運動員精神”，可惜說錯了，\N在日語中這兩句話聽上去只有一個格助詞的區別而已）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（可惜!!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才傘差點翻轉過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  覺得你有些樂在其中喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  颱風來了就好興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  或許我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點心兒砰砰跳的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:02.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（暖陽莊）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桶裡積了多少水呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮的房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些忐忑不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滴答滴答的節奏是不是快了點兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然因為今天是颱風天氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想如果桶滿了的話立刻就能換上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:07:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Good Job！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也拿出毛巾來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,防備不小心踢倒水桶時的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就完美了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄濕了真的會起火嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  晚飯怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫披薩來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每逢颱風我們家就會叫披薩來吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,披薩啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,颱風的速度有多少呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,100公里左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？是說時速？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:08:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是會更快？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三個小時就會過去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會過去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,100公里的話是從這兒到哪裡的距離呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你問的是往東走還是往西走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…山梨縣下面是甚麼縣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是靜岡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣預報在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點消失就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣明天就不能開運動會了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼颱風總是會在遠足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行啊甚麼的時候來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  由乃是個招雨的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多十次裡面有五次吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,招雨的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？是因為我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃是會喚來暴風雨的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可高興不起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（快放  倒退  播放  停止）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡100公里會到哪裡去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順便一提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山梨的東邊是東京和崎玉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而北邊和西邊是長野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大夥兒都要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是免了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去沏茶來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋  stop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停電？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多去倒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  得小心些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不要那麼大呼小叫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說很感謝你們擔心我這房間的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為如果起火的話可不止是這房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那這麼做行麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  大家閃開些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部在這裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把這些扔到哪裡去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就都放心了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  扔哪裡去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…總之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先傳給由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是小宮不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學你也冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  很熱嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得有點發熱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是淋濕了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是會起火的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乾燥劑是弄濕了就會起火的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼扔到雨裡去會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說了會起火吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是會澆滅火的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小宮  不要了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說了不能做危險的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒燒起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來  宮子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過後你得好好給我收拾掉喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是我房間的院子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我差不多該走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一趟DaDa超市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  購物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去DaDa超市嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  必須去趟大賣場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Berry店只是便利店而已呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說不知道明天能不能開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是先去買做便當的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非還有我們的一份？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我就打算做四人份的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你幫我們做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,購物甚麼的就讓我來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃真是个好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宮子你也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不大光顧這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為從暖陽莊到這裡有些遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可比Berry店便宜的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要做甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「嘗遍白色食材」的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還能加上這些嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:05.38,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（魚片）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我再去找些白色的東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要砂糖的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許飲料也是白色的好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明膠？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是透明的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:42.00,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,只限眼前  隨時都可以放心  二三屋\N二三屋白巧克力  199日圓(含稅)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還要買零食嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是白巧克力所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒…說過有關係啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:51.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,大男人豆腐  252日圓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.89,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,二三屋白巧克力  199日圓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已經好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我看過一圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是看？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:02.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,白長鬚鯨  609日圓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:07.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,合計  3049日圓  (消費稅  145日圓)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,合計是三千零四十九日圓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  從這裡抽一張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想來？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是是是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒中？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寫著秋刀魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看這個看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您…您好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天為甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  因為來了颱風
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看這邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看狀況的話就請在颱風刮得正猛的時候來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在颱風基本過去了你才來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要在颱風的日子出門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是您的想法我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們也一直是縮在房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火鍋？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雲層之上已經放晴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧  雲層之上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藍天和白雲一望無際
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想在綿綿的雲層之上散步嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  理解理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想嘗嘗味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  也有這想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:45.70,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,烤白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:50.94,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,熱騰騰  好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:58.76,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,烤白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能「嗖」地一下飛上去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會很愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…住102號房的是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是媽媽那裡寄來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是甚麼是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被這玩意裹著的栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像還是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沙英學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做栗子飯甚麼的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  用甚麼弄開這栗子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  我去拿球棒來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  沙英學姐  Let's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 我來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來個上拋球喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  栗子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋之味的代表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像還沒吃過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  秋刀魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以拿去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也是別人給的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚做成鹽烤魚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易抽中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起讓她拿走栗子來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然送出秋刀魚好些吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好尷尬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家都那麼說的話就不好不給了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是受她不少照顧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切  可恨的房東
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,房東  是房東嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暖陽莊的房東？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都…都沒能好好打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  由乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒見過房東啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是明天去一下房東那兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說了沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正明天回來之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃就累得動彈不得了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天可是運動會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雨要停了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能輸喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是針對白組嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙動不動就跑來和我較勁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想聽那傢伙的尖聲怪笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天得吃得飽飽的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後早點睡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了明天做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有運動會了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,設想最壞的情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抑制一下進食量比較妥當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的  尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又沒有吃秋刀魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  吃了烤白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋  栗子越削越小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅組加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼甚麼甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難以啟齒的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有點覺得像是看錯了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算沒有看錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也就能明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,煮得不錯  味道香濃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你碗裡不還有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,預約
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要預約
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說甚麼預約…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等你吃完了再約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就預約一下預約的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做甚麼小宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,預約的預約的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概還有十二個小時左右
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,操場會乾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不能扯大家後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺壓力巨大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆中止就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這麼懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要和大家一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就沒有問題了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:21:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮  栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,10月12日  完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,運動會加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按門鈴她不回話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敲門也沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐的房間裡飄來了可口的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.47,0:23:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  還似乎見不得人一樣端送飯菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:23:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:24:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是躲債主吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.70,0:24:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次是「3月13日  3%的希望」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.30,0:24:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在暖陽莊等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要來看哦
